encode

public com.sun.xml.ws.api.pipe.ContentType encode(com.sun.xml.ws.api.message.Packet packet,
                                                  java.io.OutputStream out)
                                           throws java.io.IOException
Encode an outgoing DIME message. The endpoint method should have a DimeOutput annotation to indicate that is actually wants DIME format. Otherwise, the message will be sent as SOAP 1.1 over HTTP.
